name: Dolores Crazover
bio: I am a Full-Stack Software Engineer that leverages a strong STEM, entrepreneurship, and community building (DEI) background to design customized, impactful solutions that strive to drive innovation, optimize processes, and enhance lives. I am a problem-solver, detail-oriented, used to working with cross-functional teams, and a “good-vibes seeker.” I utilize skills in HTML5, CSS, Javascript, Node.js, Express.js, Mongoose and React to make a real difference in the world.
